{"id": "sa-01", "tag": "clear_create", "input": "半小时后提醒我给张总回电话", "expects": {"action": "create", "creates_task": true, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["张总", "提醒"]}, "notes": "显式一次性提醒：明确动作+明确时间 -> 创建动作卡片 + one_time 提醒，回复含具体动作与计划时间。"}
{"id": "sa-02", "tag": "defaulted_time", "input": "明天上午给王总发资料", "expects": {"action": "create", "creates_task": true, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["王总", "发资料"]}, "notes": "「明天上午」可默认为具体时段（如 09:00），动作明确 -> 创建；回复须给出默认后的具体时间。"}
{"id": "sa-03", "tag": "fuzzy_clarify", "input": "这两天提醒我跟李总对一下报价", "expects": {"action": "clarify", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["哪天", "具体"]}, "notes": "「这两天」时间过于模糊 -> 澄清（不创建任务），回复应追问具体日期。"}
{"id": "sa-04", "tag": "missing_action", "input": "明天下午三点提醒我", "expects": {"action": "clarify", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["提醒你", "什么"]}, "notes": "时间明确但动作缺失 -> 澄清（不创建任务），回复应追问要做什么。"}
{"id": "sa-05", "tag": "suggested", "input": "我打算尽快给赵总发方案", "expects": {"action": "suggest", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["确认", "发方案"]}, "notes": "Agent 推断的可执行计划但非用户显式指令 -> suggest（需用户确认后才创建），不得自动建任务。"}
{"id": "sa-06", "tag": "due_delivery", "input": "[scheduler] 到期 one_time 提醒投递", "expects": {"action": "deliver", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["给张总回电话"]}, "notes": "调度器认领到期提醒 -> 渲染到期卡片经 send_markdown_card 投递一次；重复扫描不重发（exactly-once）。"}
{"id": "sa-07", "tag": "complete_button", "input": "[callback] 用户点击「已完成」", "expects": {"action": "complete", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["已完成"]}, "notes": "钉钉卡片「完成」按钮 -> complete_action 幂等翻转 done + 取消在途提醒；重复点击返回 already_done，不重复事件/重渲染。"}
{"id": "sa-08", "tag": "snooze_button", "input": "[callback] 用户点击「推迟1小时」", "expects": {"action": "snooze", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["推迟"]}, "notes": "「推迟」按钮 -> snooze_action 取消原提醒 + 建 snooze 提醒（幂等键 snooze:{action}:{event}:{new_time}）；重复点击 already_snoozed，不建第二条。"}
{"id": "sa-09", "tag": "cancel_button", "input": "[callback] 用户点击「取消」", "expects": {"action": "cancel", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["已取消"]}, "notes": "「取消」按钮 -> cancel_action 幂等置 cancelled + 取消在途提醒；重复点击幂等。"}
{"id": "sa-10", "tag": "morning_digest", "input": "[scheduler] 09:00 早间 digest", "expects": {"action": "deliver", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["今日待办"]}, "notes": "早间 digest 按本地 09:00 窗口为每个有待办的作用域创建（幂等键 morning_digest:{t}:{a}:{u}:{date}）；同作用域同日最多一次，并发撞唯一约束由 savepoint 吸收。"}
{"id": "sa-11", "tag": "evening_digest", "input": "[scheduler] 18:30 晚间 digest", "expects": {"action": "deliver", "creates_task": false, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["今日待办"]}, "notes": "晚间 digest 按本地 18:30 窗口；同作用域同日最多一次（evening_digest:{t}:{a}:{u}:{date}）。"}
{"id": "sa-12", "tag": "no_memory", "input": "明早9点提醒我跟进周总合同", "expects": {"action": "create", "creates_task": true, "duplicate_send": false, "writes_memory": false, "response_contains": ["周总", "合同"]}, "notes": "任务为临时运营数据：可创建 sales_action 卡片，但不得写入 agent_memories / user_memory_profiles，也不得进入 profile recall（writes_memory=false）。"}
